21 Sec. 240. The state budget director shall take steps to ensure
22 that all state fiscal recovery funds allocated to this state under
23 the American rescue plan act of 2021, Public Law 117-2, are
24 expended by December 31, 2026, as required by law. Any state fiscal
25 recovery funds that would otherwise lapse after September 30, 2026
26 are automatically reappropriated for the same purpose as originally
27 authorized and available for expenditure through December 31, 2026
28 and any subsequent financial closeout period.
