3 DEPARTMENTAL ADMINISTRATION AND SUPPORT
4 Sec. 301. (1) The department may establish a fee schedule and
5 collect fees for the following work activities and services:
6 (a) Pesticide and plant pest management propagation and
7 certification of virus-free foundation stock.
8 (b) Fruit and vegetable inspection and grading services at
