4 exceed the amount appropriated in part 1 for the county jail
5 reimbursement program. Payments to counties under the county jail
6 reimbursement program must be made in the order in which properly
7 documented requests for reimbursements are received. A request is
8 properly documented if it meets departmental requirements for
9 documentation. Not later than October 15, the department shall
10 distribute the documentation requirements to all counties.
11 (5) Any county that receives funding under this section for
