20 intrusion response program. The vapor intrusion response program
21 shall assess risks to public health at vapor intrusion sites and
22 respond to vapor intrusion risks if appropriate. The goals of the
23 vapor intrusion response program must include reducing the number
24 of individuals who are exposed to toxic substances through vapor
25 intrusion and improving health outcomes for individuals who are
26 identified as having been exposed to vapor intrusion.
