26 non-driving factors used in calculations or formulas in personal
27 automobile insurance rate setting. The contract must be established
28 through a competitive bidding process and the contract with a
29 university or research institute must not have any current or
ERE S06102'26 (S-1) 9n6epi

532
1 previous relationship with automobile insurance companies. The
