7 appropriation under this part or part 1 must provide an annual
8 report to the standard report recipients detailing federal policy
9 changes that do, or are expected to do, any of the following:
10 (a) Affect the operations of the department, including
11 reductions in federal revenue. For federal revenue reductions, the
12 annual report must detail the impact on the department or agency
