5 for talent partnerships. Remaining funds must be awarded in
6 accordance with this section and, as necessary, prorated based on
7 availability of funds.
8 (15) The department shall ensure grant agreements with
9 applicants include regular progress reports and clawback provisions
10 to verify that all expenditures are made in accordance with an
