21 services and advocacy, through in-person and virtual meetings, that
22 enables the organization to meet performance goals established in
23 the grant agreement.
24 (c) Fosters innovative and transformative approaches and
25 techniques for the grantee to use when providing services,
26 advocacy, and outreach for veterans and their dependents.
