26 under this part, provide a report to the chairpersons of the house
27 and senate appropriations committees, the house and senate fiscal
28 agencies, and the state budget office that details all of the
29 following:
ERE S06102'26 (S-1) 9n6epi

869
1 (i) The type of funding received.
2 (ii) When the funding was received.
3 (iii) The amount of funding received.
