5 specified purpose.
6 (c) Not later than February 15, provide a report to the
7 chairpersons of the house and senate appropriations committees, the
8 house and senate fiscal agencies, and the state budget office with
9 an estimate of funding authorized by this part that the department
10 anticipates it will receive in the subsequent fiscal year,
