5 (b) The local grade separation fund.
6 (c) The infrastructure projects authority fund.
7 (d) The comprehensive transportation fund.
8 (e) The Michigan transportation fund.
9 (f) The state aeronautics fund.
10 (g) The contracting opportunity loan fund.
11 (h) The local bridge fund.
12 (i) The movable bridge fund.
13 (j) The intercity bus equipment and facility fund.
14 (k) The rail freight fund.
15 (l) The recreation improvement fund.
16 (m) The neighborhood roads fund.
17 (n) The maritime and port fund.
18 (o) The Blue Water Bridge fund.
