21 transportation economic development fund and local bridge fund may
22 receive federal, local, or private funds or restricted source funds
23 such as interest earnings.
24 (5) None of the funds statutorily dedicated to the
25 transportation economic development fund and local bridge fund
26 shall be diverted to other projects.
