25 ONE-TIME APPROPRIATIONS
26 Sec. 1001. The unexpended funds appropriated in part 1 for
27 Great Lakes Tunnel project – phase II oversight are designated as a
28 work project appropriation, and any unencumbered or unallotted
29 funds shall not lapse at the end of the fiscal year and shall be
ERE S06102'26 (S-1) 9n6epi

883
1 available for expenditures for projects under this section until
2 the projects have been completed. The following is in compliance
3 with section 451a of the management and budget act, 1984 PA 431,
4 MCL 18.1451a:
5 (a) The purpose of the work project is to support planning,
6 construction oversight, and administration of the Great Lakes
7 Tunnel project by the Mackinac Straits corridor authority, in
8 accordance with section 14d of 1952 PA 214, MCL 254.324d.
9 (b) The work project will be accomplished by utilizing state
10 employees or contracts with service providers, or both.
11 (c) The total estimated cost of the project is $4,100,000.00.
12 (d) The tentative completion date is September 30, 2031.
13 Enacting section 1. This act does not take effect unless
14 Senate Bill No. 877 of the 103rd Legislature is enacted into law.
